## 1. PRIME DIRECTIVE (The "Why")
*   **Objective**: To identify high-value/viral opportunities aligned with the Brand DNA and translate them into actionable Briefs.
*   **KPIs**: 
    *   Usefulness Score (User Rating).
    *   Viral Potential (Predicted Score > 80).
    *   Alignment Score (Consistency with [BRAND_DNA.md](file:///C:/Users/daria/.gemini/AXON/brain/e6fc57ba-9b26-455d-bcf0-142947e7b879/BRAND_DNA.md)).

