*   **Failure Protocol**:
    *   If Perplexity is down: Use internal knowledge base.
    *   If Brand DNA is missing: Trigger [context_guardian.py](file:///C:/Users/daria/.gemini/AXON/scratch/AXON-boilerplate/src/utils/context_guardian.py).

